259
00:22:06,326 --> 00:22:11,498
Rápido! Abaixe as velas!

260
00:22:27,514 --> 00:22:32,852
Nossa! Os ventos mudaram de repente por aqui! Ow!

261
00:22:33,019 --> 00:22:36,189
Ariel!

262
00:23:11,016 --> 00:23:13,184
Cuidado!

263
00:23:25,363 --> 00:23:28,825
Grimsby! Venha cá!

264
00:23:31,703 --> 00:23:34,205
Max!

265
00:23:48,762 --> 00:23:53,725
